      "Warpick: Fextralife classifies as Hammer weapon class but primary damage is Pierce (unusual mismatch)",
      "Falchion: drop rate not specified on Fextralife page (null)",
      "Torch: 'No Skill' Ash of War only applies; conventional AoW infusion unavailable (special case of canInfuse=false)"
    ]
